{"type": "article", "id": 63711, "title": "萤光灯管与混凝土块的组合，可以玩出多少花样？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-05-13T22:54:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 58531, "name": "Wild Architectural Objects"}, {"id": 13757, "name": "Bang & Olufsen"}, {"id": 58532, "name": "Butler Lindgård"}, {"id": 58533, "name": "Morgane Tschiember"}, {"id": 939, "name": "Jasper Morrison"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 112, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190513194809oLEVGvf2byQ05hIi.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #101010; -webkit-text-stroke: #101010} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #101010; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #101010} span.s6 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none; background-color: #ffffff} </style>  </p><h3>Corks by Jasper Morrison </h3><p>最近，英国极简主义设计师 Jasper Morrison 在纽约切尔西的 Kasmin 画廊办了一个软木主题的家具展，这也是其在北美的首个个展。</p><p>这个名为 Corks 的展览汇集了 Jasper Morrison 的软木家具作品，展出的物品包括躺椅、书架、餐桌、椅子、凳子、矮桌、长凳和软木壁炉。所选材料均是从葡萄酒瓶软木塞生产中留下的软木块材料切割物。</p><p>整个画廊空间的一个区域被配置为家庭环境。在这里，墙壁被涂成深绿色，另有手绘的他本人的家具作品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513194846WtZMJEk2KU5laDNO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513194846dVUAxyY2k53RfX7q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513194847VQZ29ldjLXcUG1IW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513194848JQk2zuNAHB36nyG1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513194850KW1u2cLGF4DnygBm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332910\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905131948543oUjPznT2yl0b6cY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513194855kW2gIbMrNOZDLCpd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333756\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513194858sJmKd4yit0cH6SB5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2019/05/13/jasper-morrison-corks-furniture-kasmin/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Open Space by Morgane Tschiember</h3><p>法国艺术家Morgane Tschiember 的系列作品 Open Space ，是混凝土和灯管塑造外型简洁而带诗意的光之雕塑，混凝土块与灯光线条的组合，在不同的视角下构成截然不同的画面。</p><p>萤光灯管与混凝土块，两者形态与线条并置构成发光的剪影。可见的材料在空气中描绘几何边界，Morgane Tschiember 试着以光填入其中的空间虚无。</p><p>系列作之一的 Open Space 5 ，正面看似只是结合圆形与方形的几何造型，从侧面一看却发现作品拉开了景深，在有限的空间尺度内创造细节变化。</p><p>Open Space 4 则是直立的锯齿状混凝土和灯管，灯光带来的阴影线条为作品增添趣味；类似的作品 Open Space 2 以阶梯造型呈现，灯管之间的距离却拉近了，光晕营造出朦胧的效果，有别于其他纯粹线性造型带来的感受。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195138xaPEkoHcTGwtZYsJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.590741\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195028h1R0CH6tMziWUsEm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.055000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195029RUPcdDv68JLKXeqy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195029jfVqGlALHYOEpDTn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195030qW39HgBFcZt6hRmd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195030PU73GELMTxDrW5F6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195030qnZFgR8svmQ0op7a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.245000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195031ruft9VX5RdocleYG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195031Sz1VMjC60oW5fXil.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195031kRYZO547KGSwJ0rl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195032qpD9JZ0SvR63KngH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>E6 &amp; E8 by Bang &amp; Olufsen</h3><p>丹麦音响品牌 Bang &amp; Olufsen 宣布将品牌旗下 Beoplay 系列 E6 和 E8 的耳机改进升级，优化了在高强度运动锻炼时的性能表现。</p><p>两款 IP54 级别防水防汗的耳机此次得到软件硬件的提升：声效方面，B&amp;O 推出一款 App 帮助耳机增强重低音性能；外形上，E8 真无线运动耳机新增一款白色皮面的铝制充电盒和数款不同的鱼鳍形耳部贴合配件提高舒适度，E6 则采用拒水连接线，双耳添加磁性吸附特性以便收纳，品牌 logo 和控制按键都采用拉丝铝质感。</p><p>同时，一款圆形 Beoplay 无线充电板也随著两款耳机一起发布，设计和耳机完美匹配。Beoplay E6 Motion 和 Beoplay E8 Motion 的售价分别为 360 美元和 390 美元，<a href=\"https://www.bang-olufsen.com/en/headphones\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195226NH34TWI9gOPUZLjv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195226yUkFV6ZnhCTjLltv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195227X7uOcGljzHDErK5V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195227sxUHV2Ncaf8QBZ36.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195227FvCyzML2G0l76SEB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019051319522998nz1G7vMKrkxRSQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195227apKYHMr5SXAebli8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lily by Wild Architectural Objects </h3><p>最近，在法国未来世界影视城 40 米的甲板上，出现了一个名为 Lily 的装置项目，由 Wild Architectural Objects 团队操刀设计。</p><p>这个装置由五个浮标组成，每个浮标配备四个蹦床。设计团队将 Lily 安装在未来世界主题公园的中心湖上，成为了一个妙趣横生的全新能量转化场所。</p><p>有些游客可能需要在水边薄夹板上步行一会才能平息其它景点带来的激动心情。而这里的游客则有了和在长椅上调整呼吸完全不同的选择，在充满阳光的宁静场地呼吸半空中的清新空气。</p><p>Lily 由1000 平方米的帆布和 450 立方米的蹦床空气组成。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195305m0KhNaWMpFjq8yYi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195305g1pivtqHjFzBDlwx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.621027\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905131953057nPYQkl41pth8xZN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195306iq0AYoI5RmvSH7B2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.696822\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905131953060YAnHJLzNR57KdPe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195306lLCroBOMj7fvmxka.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195307720a5z4YKAhu3ixv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Nipple, Hairy, Traces and Stained by Butler Lindgård </h3><p>瑞典设计二人组 Butler Lindgård 创造了灵感源于女性身体的纺织品系列 Tits N Ass，包括四种图形图案：乳头，毛发，痕迹和染色。每一个都涉及一个挑战大众对女性身体的问题，如母乳喂养、体毛、超重和月经。</p><p>这些设计适用于地毯、亚麻布、枕垫和靠垫，以及纺织墙面和印花。比如瑞典地毯公司 Kasthall 生产的手工簇绒乳头地毯，Traces 亚麻布等等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195341uyAvUJa31m5wXN0g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619289\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195346EhsxMXfkCdnoIFwV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195356vbUh6ydC2AogtI10.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.046531\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195358ky7PVNjLcElSe1XF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.432741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195358a0LHUieDF9ykoVvl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.879865\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195402faLQJDvGHqV4K7l0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195410U3ZbyGYSsfrTt6um.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.735618\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905131954217SVeZ4JQCtRYk8uy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562630\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190513195422aiCNlGq7ZtKxQTjU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769882\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://butlerlindgard.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Butler Lindgård</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"medium-insert-active\"><br></p>"}